turn it off?

05:09.476 --> 05:11.569
All right,
you guys, come on.

05:11.646 --> 05:12.966
Backpacks, lunches.

05:13.033 --> 05:14.570
Homework. Let's go.

05:15.480 --> 05:16.937
- Let's go.
- Hold on.

05:17.014 --> 05:19.130
