You're not pregnant.

05:45.367 --> 05:47.668
Yeah, I... well,
I know that now. I...

05:47.745 --> 05:49.528
Didn't you hear anything
that Dr. Roper said?

05:49.605 --> 05:50.855
Yeah.

05:50.938 --> 05:53.736
