I gotta get an Uber.

09:04.688 --> 09:06.262
Where you going?

09:06.873 --> 09:08.148
To Joshua Tree.

09:08.225 --> 09:09.815
To my women's moon circle.

09:09.892 --> 09:11.296
I invited you, remember?

09:11.373 --> 09:12.862
