09:13.842 --> 09:15.793
Yeah, I'm sorry about that.

09:15.870 --> 09:17.170
It's fine.

09:17.795 --> 09:19.457
It's too bad, though.

09:19.638 --> 09:21.359
I mean, I just had
this intuition

09:21.436 --> 09:23.720
that you really needed
some guidance, but...

09:38.847 --> 09:40.962
What is a moon circle, exactly?

09:42.232 --> 09:44.223
New moons represent beginnings.

09:44.308 --> 09:48.198
It's a time for planting seeds
and setting intentions,

09:48.275 --> 09:52.519
and then committing to behaviors
to help us manifest them.

09:53.006 --> 09:55.117
And I'm really looking
forward to this one,

09:55.194 --> 09:56.685
because Gaelle
is going to be there.

09:56.762 --> 09:57.970
Who's Gaelle?

09:58.388 --> 09:59.690
She's my guru.

09:59.767 --> 10:01.387
She's a healer.

10:01.490 --> 10:03.070
She's a true gift.

10:03.147 --> 10:05.232
I mean, my work with her
has been so transformative,

10:05.309 --> 10:07.191
I don't even see
my therapist anymore.

10:12.303 --> 10:13.975
Fuck it.

10:15.813 --> 10:17.314
I'll go.

10:18.154 --> 10:20.429
- For real?
- For real.

10:21.397 --> 10:23.230
Oh, my God. Awesome.

10:24.439 --> 10:27.322
You sure Vik
won't mind us borrowing his car?

10:27.399 --> 10:31.186
Um, he might, but I don't
particularly care at the moment.

10:33.097 --> 10:35.199
What kind of music
do you like?

10:35.615 --> 10:38.418
Oh, I think probably nothing
that you would like.

10:38.576 --> 10:39.945
Try me.

10:40.623 --> 10:41.690
Uh, I don't know.

10:41.767 --> 10:42.815
I like rock music.

10:42.892 --> 10:44.399
I like some folk music.

10:44.476 --> 10:45.529
Patti Smith?

10:45.606 --> 10:47.186
Uh, sure.

10:48.326 --> 10:50.606
She's my favorite
when I'm super depressed.

10:50.683 --> 10:52.427
Probably listened
to this album

10:52.504 --> 10:54.606
like 500 times
in the past week.

10:54.683 --> 10:57.278
- Why were you super depressed?
- Um...

10:59.597 --> 11:01.996
I fucked a married man.

11:02.980 --> 11:06.335
I'm really annoyed
with myself

11:06.412 --> 11:09.950
because I've done it before,
and it never ends well for me.

11:10.027 --> 11:11.365
I see.

11:11.879 --> 11:14.271
And I even know his wife,

11:14.348 --> 11:15.615
and I...

11:15.938 --> 11:18.324
I really like his wife, so...

11:19.701 --> 11:21.255
it was a stupid thing to do.

11:21.332 --> 11:22.569
Why did you do it?

11:22.646 --> 11:24.565
My mom broke up
like two marriages,

11:24.642 --> 11:28.070
so I guess I just always thought
that's how you vet a man,

11:28.147 --> 11:30.232
like how you know
if he's stable or not.

11:30.309 --> 11:32.629
You mean, if he's married
to someone else?

11:32.712 --> 11:33.828
Yeah, like,

11:33.905 --> 11:34.935
